<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>when creating a controller with Zend_Tool with multiple words, the views/scripts folder isn't named correctly.</p>

<p>Example:</p>

<p>./zf.sh create controller supplyAndDemand
provides:
controller name: SupplyAndDemandController
controller filename: (application/controllers/)SupplyAndDemandController.php
view/scripts folder: (application/views/)supplyAndDemand</p>

<p>But the dispatcher searches for a view script in the application/views/supply-and-demand folder, instead of application/views/supplyAndDemand</p>

    </div>
</div>

